description:
C.H.A.O.S.Tournament.HD-1.2.2[Android][Nan1977]


Release date: July 8, 2013
 Genre: Simulation helicopter
 Developer: SKYJET INTERNATIONAL
 Format:. Apk, cache
 Version: 1.2.2
 Language: English


System requirements:
 ==========================

 OS Version: Android 2.3 +; Processor Type: ARMv7



 CHAOS Tournament - this is an opportunity to pass a new military adventure in the sky, but in a more rigid and competitive environment. If you are an experienced pilot - test your combat skills by fighting in the strict rules of our tournaments with those who already have significant experience in the management of helicopter gunships. If you are a beginner - to prove that you are a rising star, or ... or a falling star from the sky.


Setting:
 ==========================

 1) Copy com.skyjet.chaosarenahd folder to sdcard / Android / obb

 2) Install APK

 3) Play!
